This is the scratch_radio-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the scratch_radio blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'scratch_radio', which is imported as:

    import scratch_radio

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(scratch_radio)
